1ï¸âƒ£ Professional Sequence Diagram (Plan Approval Flow)

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Maker
    actor Checker
    actor Controller
    participant System as BC & OR Workflow Engine
    participant DB as Database

    Maker->>System: Create Plan (Draft)
    System->>DB: Save Plan
    DB-->>System: Plan Stored
    System-->>Maker: Draft Saved

    Maker->>System: Submit Plan
    System->>DB: Update Status = SUBMITTED
    System->>Checker: Notification Triggered

    Checker->>System: Review Plan

    alt Rejected by Checker
        System->>DB: Update Status = REJECTED
        System-->>Maker: Return with Remarks
    else Approved by Checker
        System->>DB: Update Status = CHECKER_APPROVED
        System->>Controller: Forward for Final Approval
    end

    Controller->>System: Final Review

    alt Rejected by Controller
        System->>DB: Update Status = REJECTED
        System-->>Maker: Return with Remarks
    else Approved by Controller
        System->>DB: Update Status = APPROVED
        System-->>Maker: Plan Fully Approved
    end

âœ… Improvements:

Autonumbered steps

Database interaction shown

Clear status transitions

Enterprise-level clarity



