2ï¸âƒ£ Swimlane Activity Diagram (End-to-End Workflow)

This version separates responsibilities by role.

flowchart LR

subgraph Maker
    M1[Create Plan]
    M2[Submit Plan]
    M3[Modify Plan]
end

subgraph Checker
    C1[Review Plan]
    C2{Approve?}
end

subgraph Controller
    CT1[Final Review]
    CT2{Approve?}
end

subgraph System
    S1[Update Status]
    S2[Send Notification]
end

Start((Start)) --> M1
M1 --> M2
M2 --> S1
S1 --> S2
S2 --> C1

C1 --> C2
C2 -- Reject --> S1
S1 --> M3
M3 --> M2

C2 -- Approve --> S1
S1 --> CT1
CT1 --> CT2

CT2 -- Reject --> S1
CT2 -- Approve --> End((Plan Approved))

âœ… Why this is better:

Clear role segregation

Workflow engine shown

Loop handling included

Presentation-friendly



